caption: The image is a promotional poster for a toy drive event in Larana community. The event is scheduled for December 21, 2022, from 08:00 to 16:00. The poster encourages people to donate toys for children so they can enjoy Christmas this year. The image features a cute snowman as the main visual element, with the words "Larana community" written on the bottom right corner.
original_title: Green and Gold Modern Toy Drive Instagram Story
texts: Get the kids present so they can enjoy Christmas this year.
